{
  "Description": "Deploy SLURM cluster with N (default=2) compute nodes + 1 login node to run micro benchmarks of MPI.\nOn each node, run chef-solo:\n$ sudo chef-solo -j /etc/chef/configure-runlist.json\nOnce the cluster is up, login to the login node and run:\n$ salloc -N2 -c<CPUs> mpirun /usr/local/libexec/osu-micro-benchmarks/mpi/pt2pt/osu_latency\n", 
